Package: TreeDist
Title: Distances between Phylogenetic Trees
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Martin R.", 'Smith',
                  email="martin.smith@durham.ac.uk", 
                  role=c("aut", "cre", "cph", "prg"), 
                  comment=c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5660-1727")),
             person("Roy", "Jonker", email="roy_jonker@magiclogic.com",
                  role = "prg"),
             person("Harold", "Cooper", email="hbc@mit.edu", role = "ctb"),
             person("Yong", "Yang", email="yongyanglink@gmail.com", role="ctb")
            )
License: GPL (>= 3)
Description: Implements measures of tree similarity, including 
  Information-based generalized Robinson-Foulds distances
  (Mutual Phylogenetic Information, Mutual Clustering Information; Smith, in revision); 
  the metric of Nye et al. (2006) <doi:10.1093/bioinformatics/bti720>;
  the Matching Split Distance (Bogdanowicz & Giaro 2012) <doi:10.1109/TCBB.2011.48>;
  the Kendall-Colijn (2016) distance <doi:10.1093/molbev/msw124>, and the
  Nearest Neighbour Interchange (NNI) distance, approximated per Li et al. 1996
  <doi:10.1007/3-540-61332-3_168>.
Copyright: Incorporates Jonker-Volgenant Linear Assignment Problem 
  implementation by Roy Jonker, modified by Harold Cooper and Yong Yang.
URL: https://ms609.github.io/TreeDist, https://github.com/ms609/TreeDist
